==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Dib
<hw>Dib</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One of the small bones in
the knee joints of sheep uniting the bones above and below the
joints.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <def>A child's game, played with dib
bones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dibasic</ent>⟦br⟧
